 {
  "text": "Good evening, passengers, and welcome to Washington Dulles International Airport. Please have your passport and boarding pass ready for immigration. All arriving passengers must go through passport control before collecting their baggage. If you have nothing to declare, follow the green signs to customs. If you are carrying goods to declare, please use the red channel. The baggage claim for flight two-one-four is at carousel five. Please keep your luggage with you at all times. We wish you a pleasant stay, and thank you for flying with us.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a11_listening_announcement.mp3"
 },
 {
